The '''Columus Tourism Board''' was a [[Columi/Legends|Columi]] government organization based out of [[Bailee]], [[Columus/Legends|Columus]] that was charged with attracting tourists to the planet.

Shortly before the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] began, it came under fire from physicians like [[Gidoo Zehow]] for claiming that Columi's low-gravity environment had therapeutic effects for the overweight.

